cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.PL, cs.SE 

This paper discusses cost-based query optimizers, which are a fundamental component of database management systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Database). The paper also discusses improvements to cost models and cardinality estimation, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also proposes a re-optimization mechanism, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE).
